<div style="max-width:740px;margin:0 auto;padding:3rem 1.5rem">
  <h1 style="font-size:2rem;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:1.5rem">About NickPicks</h1>
  <p style="margin-bottom:1.25rem;line-height:1.75">NickPicks exists because most product review sites are either SEO-stuffed content farms or undisclosed paid placements. We are neither.</p>
  <p style="margin-bottom:1.25rem;line-height:1.75">We publish honest, independently researched buying guides and product reviews across five categories: home office, luxury beauty, fitness, kitchen, and pet tech. Our goal is simple: help you buy the right thing once instead of the wrong thing twice.</p>
  <h2 style="font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:700;margin:2rem 0 0.75rem">How We Research</h2>
  <ul style="margin:0.75rem 0 1rem 1.5rem;line-height:1.75">
    <li>We read hundreds of verified buyer reviews across platforms</li>
    <li>We compare manufacturer specs and independent lab test data where available</li>
    <li>We cross-reference pricing, warranty terms, and long-term reliability data</li>
    <li>We rank by real-world value, not commission rate</li>
  </ul>
  <h2 style="font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:700;margin:2rem 0 0.75rem">Affiliate Disclosure</h2>
  <p style="line-height:1.75">We participate in the Amazon Associates Program and may earn commissions when you buy through our links. This never influences our rankings. See our full <a href="{{ '/affiliate-disclosure/' | url }}">affiliate disclosure</a>.</p>
